Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw bared her front row of jagged teeth. "No." She refused the 
drink. She took a step back, feeling trapped by the group of 
Predacons, even her own kind.

She didn't understand none of this. All these faction didn't make 
sense to her. It was so much more simpiler in the past. Perhaps she 
was better in the Wild.
